snippet.title: The Agenda with Steve Paikin
snippet.description: The Agenda with Steve Paikin is TVO's flagship current affairs program, devoted to exploring the social, political, cultural, and economic issues that are changing our world. We consistently offer a diversity of viewpoints and in-depth analysis of what lies behind the headlines.
